  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/ed8d6269e596e12372a22c2159ffb970.poster.avif?t=1726816560\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/ed8d6269e596e12372a22c2159ffb970.webm?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/ed8d6269e596e12372a22c2159ffb970.mp4?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>∠ Prepare for an adrenaline-pumping and immersive VR experience that combines fast-paced combat and strategic rune drawing inspired by Slavic mythology. The fate of the sanctuary and the whole world, is in your hands<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/a262724f18ab174a77f75c495aaf3d5e.poster.avif?t=1726816560\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/a262724f18ab174a77f75c495aaf3d5e.webm?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/a262724f18ab174a77f75c495aaf3d5e.mp4?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>∠ Plunge into the world of Slavic mythology and take on the role of a brave shaman in this immersive roguelike VR Wave Shooter. Defend the holy shrine of the god \"Veles\" from relentless waves of monstrous creatures summoned by the powerful rival \"Perun\" in easy to pick up but hard to master short gaming sessions<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/5c552d21d781e1ba35a6349ca3847869.poster.avif?t=1726816560\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/5c552d21d781e1ba35a6349ca3847869.webm?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/5c552d21d781e1ba35a6349ca3847869.mp4?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/8ef752f90282ce87f5c0750c70f87ece.poster.avif?t=1726816560\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/8ef752f90282ce87f5c0750c70f87ece.webm?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/8ef752f90282ce87f5c0750c70f87ece.mp4?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>∠ Your shamanic body may be frail, but your bending powers are not. Armed with the power of ancient runes master the elements of nature fire, water, earth and air<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/6662dddde5949263adcbbb9362d076ec.poster.avif?t=1726816560\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/6662dddde5949263adcbbb9362d076ec.webm?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/6662dddde5949263adcbbb9362d076ec.mp4?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/c6783a18df4378bdaf33460079b6cf6f.poster.avif?t=1726816560\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/c6783a18df4378bdaf33460079b6cf6f.webm?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/c6783a18df4378bdaf33460079b6cf6f.mp4?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>∠ Draw various runes with an intuitive spellcasting system using the elemental Runepads. <br>Cast powerful spells by solely moving your hands<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/2a976c8dfd369a6c748b5a7626f5b0b0.poster.avif?t=1726816560\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/2a976c8dfd369a6c748b5a7626f5b0b0.webm?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/2a976c8dfd369a6c748b5a7626f5b0b0.mp4?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/efb666796d62b3e4e73922a2bd51d542.poster.avif?t=1726816560\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/efb666796d62b3e4e73922a2bd51d542.webm?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/efb666796d62b3e4e73922a2bd51d542.mp4?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>∠ Discover and master 16 different elemental spells.  <br>Use them against Perun's dark creatures to exploit their weaknesses <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/2ffb938a46aa0ae55c96d9bdc2a610f6.poster.avif?t=1726816560\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/2ffb938a46aa0ae55c96d9bdc2a610f6.webm?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/2ffb938a46aa0ae55c96d9bdc2a610f6.mp4?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/75e521668e9da81982d8ea78aa9057d3.poster.avif?t=1726816560\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/75e521668e9da81982d8ea78aa9057d3.webm?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/75e521668e9da81982d8ea78aa9057d3.mp4?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/0c9f886439ae0c89c24d86e3af115f05.poster.avif?t=1726816560\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/0c9f886439ae0c89c24d86e3af115f05.webm?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/0c9f886439ae0c89c24d86e3af115f05.mp4?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>∠ Start your run with basic elemental magic and unlock new powerful spells. Upgrade any spell according to your playstyle, adding even more variety to your runs<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/e4a4c953c00b4504042668c68958bf2c.poster.avif?t=1726816560\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/e4a4c953c00b4504042668c68958bf2c.webm?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/e4a4c953c00b4504042668c68958bf2c.mp4?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/6d4b0c60b59a8e7ed93f5aa05a3b679a.poster.avif?t=1726816560\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/6d4b0c60b59a8e7ed93f5aa05a3b679a.webm?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/6d4b0c60b59a8e7ed93f5aa05a3b679a.mp4?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>∠ Use your abilities against slavic mythological creatures. The stronger the waves, the greater the challenges that require quick thinking and strategic decisions but remember that each death is temporary since each run makes you more skilled<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/ab1273c9da30e7aa7e13b18b138d20f4.poster.avif?t=1726816560\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/ab1273c9da30e7aa7e13b18b138d20f4.webm?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/ab1273c9da30e7aa7e13b18b138d20f4.mp4?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/024049db34aa24014c20744850239417.poster.avif?t=1726816560\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/024049db34aa24014c20744850239417.webm?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/024049db34aa24014c20744850239417.mp4?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>• Shamanic:          • Learn to bend elemental magic like: fire, water, earth, air<br>• Runes:                • Unlock during your run up to 16 spells<br>• Dynamic Builds: • With over 20 different upgrades to choose from throughout a run, no two attempts will ever be the same<br>• Waves:               • Learn the weaknesses of the slavic creatures and use the right spells during 15 Waves in Story Mode<br>• Pick Up & Play:  • Easy to pick up but hard to master short gaming sessions<br>• Your Playstyle:   • You choose wether to focus on your reflex, timing or strategic skills<br>• Endless Mode:   • Proof your skills in the ultimate runebending test and climb up the leaderboard<br><br>Are you ready to join this epic battle and determine the fate of the world?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/7eb7d2b5157f94282cf6c2096d878d09.poster.avif?t=1726816560\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/7eb7d2b5157f94282cf6c2096d878d09.webm?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/7eb7d2b5157f94282cf6c2096d878d09.mp4?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/08dcd31a25f9ad2e20d7cbade5c4c5c8.avif?t=1726816560\" width=170 height=174 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/ed8d6269e596e12372a22c2159ffb970.poster.avif?t=1726816560\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/ed8d6269e596e12372a22c2159ffb970.webm?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/ed8d6269e596e12372a22c2159ffb970.mp4?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>∠ Prepare for an adrenaline-pumping and immersive VR experience that combines fast-paced combat and strategic rune drawing inspired by Slavic mythology. The fate of the sanctuary and the whole world, is in your hands<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/a262724f18ab174a77f75c495aaf3d5e.poster.avif?t=1726816560\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/a262724f18ab174a77f75c495aaf3d5e.webm?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/a262724f18ab174a77f75c495aaf3d5e.mp4?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>∠ Plunge into the world of Slavic mythology and take on the role of a brave shaman in this immersive roguelike VR Wave Shooter. Defend the holy shrine of the god \"Veles\" from relentless waves of monstrous creatures summoned by the powerful rival \"Perun\" in easy to pick up but hard to master short gaming sessions<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/5c552d21d7