nesses <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/2ffb938a46aa0ae55c96d9bdc2a610f6.poster.avif?t=1726816560\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/2ffb938a46aa0ae55c96d9bdc2a610f6.webm?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/2ffb938a46aa0ae55c96d9bdc2a610f6.mp4?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/75e521668e9da81982d8ea78aa9057d3.poster.avif?t=1726816560\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/75e521668e9da81982d8ea78aa9057d3.webm?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/75e521668e9da81982d8ea78aa9057d3.mp4?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/0c9f886439ae0c89c24d86e3af115f05.poster.avif?t=1726816560\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/0c9f886439ae0c89c24d86e3af115f05.webm?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387750/extras/0c9f886439ae0c89c24d86e3af115f05.mp4?t=1726816560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>∠ Start your run with basic elemental magic and unlock new powerful spells. Upgrade any spell according to your 